{"tid":409476,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Excel if if if if 運算 問題","createTime":"2017-09-22T05:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T15:06:47.000Z","uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8d450bac71aea9b171bea2c7e1f6a5f48449fc","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"hi,是咁的, 有個關於多個 if 同時使用問題<br />\n假使一間房分 4 星期計算, 數字係收費, <br />\n第一星期   7 日: 20<br />\n第二星期 14 日: 40<br />\n第三星期 21 日: 60<br />\n第四星期 28 日: 80<br />\n<br />\n我希望 A1 數值出現 7 時, B2 會計算出為 20<br />\nA1 數值出現 14 時, B2 會計算出 40, <br />\n但唔可以用 =iferror((ifA1=7,20,if(A1=14,40),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n因為本身現實用既時候係需要用作運算用途,<br />\n我自己打條式係:<br />\n<br />\n=iferror(if(A1&gt;=7,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=14,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=21,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=28,B2*20),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n咁樣能夠做到我想要既野, 但覺得條式寫得好累聚,<br />\n有無 excel 巴打可以指點吓, 有無更簡單直接容易表達到既 if 式 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cffa729e1f447c1ff1256559615dc5fa7926b12","tid":409476,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"switch"},{"pid":"049b4c3a04ebff02a8edc7657529ca20bb1e35d6","tid":409476,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>switch</blockquote><br />\n冇睇到下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁用ifs"},{"pid":"54f6cc0f3d6c1f238f2cf82401bb84c3711e563d","tid":409476,"uid":106407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"用 lookup 好d"},{"pid":"e42c0dddc56473d1557183df63960266b2602fee","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用 lookup 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無 exsample ?? 因為我諗唔到 lookup 可以點應用係呢個計算上"},{"pid":"f16ba8710ce9cac2a39c5e9f8c2cae5feae03cb2","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>switch</blockquote><br />\n冇睇到下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁用ifs</blockquote><br />\ngoogle 左 ifs, 好似 ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陣間試吓<br />\n但最擔心係我是用 google sheet, 唔知佢有無 ifs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39affadc613bba4418edd646bbf2639380b54ac4","tid":409476,"uid":107472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"整個細表<br />\n      A       B<br />\n1    7       20<br />\n2    14     40<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後你想出計算結果個到用vlookup<br />\n例如你想你c1打7 之後d1出20<br />\n你就係d1打vlookup(c1,a1-b2,2,false)<br />\n咁就ok  好似係"},{"pid":"69444756ab953b0759af3b83389fc445251d595c","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整個細表<br />\n      A       B<br />\n1    7       20<br />\n2    14     40<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後你想出計算結果個到用vlookup<br />\n例如你想你c1打7 之後d1出20<br />\n你就係d1打vlookup(c1,a1-b2,2,false)<br />\n咁就ok  好似係</blockquote><br />\n我現實用其實係要計數, lookup 如果只係配對就未必岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eecc71646249dd5a35243ba527f001e02af3fc1","tid":409476,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>switch</blockquote><br />\n冇睇到下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁用ifs</blockquote><br />\ngoogle 左 ifs, 好似 ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陣間試吓<br />\n但最擔心係我是用 google sheet, 唔知佢有無 ifs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/docs/answer/7014145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fdocs%2Fanswer%2F7014145&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=e4068ddc\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/docs/answer/7014145</a>"},{"pid":"53a95d526c3d47f3d2688bb3f1180ad3c50a2afa","tid":409476,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"=iferror(if(A1&gt;=7,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=14,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=21,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=28,B2*20),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n唔太明你條式做緊乜<br />\nA1係日數，但點解之後B2*20?<br />\nB2係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574babf3f417246076943632fbaf09f8f3e00c43","tid":409476,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>=iferror(if(A1&gt;=7,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=14,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=21,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=28,B2*20),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n唔太明你條式做緊乜<br />\nA1係日數，但點解之後B2*20?<br />\nB2係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋20 40係一日收費定一星期？<br />\n你係咪想分段收費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1-7日 每日20<br />\n8-14日 每日40<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無get錯"},{"pid":"87894ea7a3383c88b3e458329b2d3b26313483e1","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>=iferror(if(A1&gt;=7,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=14,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=21,B2*20)+if(A1&gt;=28,B2*20),&quot;&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n唔太明你條式做緊乜<br />\nA1係日數，但點解之後B2*20?<br />\nB2係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋20 40係一日收費定一星期？<br />\n你係咪想分段收費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1-7日 每日20<br />\n8-14日 每日40<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無get錯</blockquote><br />\n係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案"},{"pid":"f1d6409fb59c4fef25d8c6382592e8d82bc94138","tid":409476,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"=A1/7*20"},{"pid":"a3b7e6efe2bfe352ccef0c16691ad3fc486f7d78","tid":409476,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"vlookup 啦仲慢慢if咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ca0e8680287e4f998078d2445a89d3ad9366da","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>vlookup 啦仲慢慢if咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有無 exsample 參考 ?"},{"pid":"2418a92109e04b51ffef90dec8f96e73cad274ce","tid":409476,"uid":36210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"唔太識excel<br />\n你係咪想要<br />\nceiling(A1/7,1)*20?"},{"pid":"0020109184fd7f2e567f33e18818011054471373","tid":409476,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案</blockquote><br />\n=B2*(MIN(MAX(0,A1-0),7)*20+MIN(MAX(0,A1-7),7)*40+MIN(MAX(0,A1-14),7)*60+MAX(0,A1-21)*80)"},{"pid":"5000898c9bfbec26bff1fbcca06abe10ee2e372a","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案</blockquote><br />\n=B2*(MIN(MAX(0,A1-0),7)*20+MIN(MAX(0,A1-7),7)*40+MIN(MAX(0,A1-14),7)*60+MAX(0,A1-21)*80)</blockquote><br />\n巴打我用你條式去做, <br />\nA1 日數: 7 日<br />\nB2 人數: 1 人<br />\nC3 收費: 20 &lt;- 呢個係 1 人收費, 如果 B2 係 2 人,<br />\n               呢格就會係 40<br />\n<br />\n但我用你條式, 佢計出黎 C3 一人情況下變左 560 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪有野搞錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573a0d9bc16ddbce9cb979334fc2c2b7a5e8beed","tid":409476,"uid":36210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案</blockquote><br />\n=B2*(MIN(MAX(0,A1-0),7)*20+MIN(MAX(0,A1-7),7)*40+MIN(MAX(0,A1-14),7)*60+MAX(0,A1-21)*80)</blockquote><br />\n巴打我用你條式去做, <br />\nA1 日數: 7 日<br />\nB2 人數: 1 人<br />\nC3 收費: 20 &lt;- 呢個係 1 人收費, 如果 B2 係 2 人,<br />\n               呢格就會係 40<br />\n<br />\n但我用你條式, 佢計出黎 C3 一人情況下變左 560 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪有野搞錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你C3打<br />\n=CEILING(A1/7,1)*B2*20<br />\n睇下係咪你想要ge野"},{"pid":"63dd77b5887b8dd169120ec8fe6fb4d523d07d54","tid":409476,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案</blockquote><br />\n=B2*(MIN(MAX(0,A1-0),7)*20+MIN(MAX(0,A1-7),7)*40+MIN(MAX(0,A1-14),7)*60+MAX(0,A1-21)*80)</blockquote><br />\n巴打我用你條式去做, <br />\nA1 日數: 7 日<br />\nB2 人數: 1 人<br />\nC3 收費: 20 &lt;- 呢個係 1 人收費, 如果 B2 係 2 人,<br />\n               呢格就會係 40<br />\n<br />\n但我用你條式, 佢計出黎 C3 一人情況下變左 560 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪有野搞錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你C3打<br />\n=CEILING(A1/7,1)*B2*20<br />\n睇下係咪你想要ge野</blockquote><br />\nok, 聽日返工試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx巴打"},{"pid":"9ca2ced06c291ddb5cc8aad7caf8e3d1f115a47e","tid":409476,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 無錯, 我條式set 係 C3 格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始唔記得打明 C3 格<br />\n我既數式係想分段收費, A1 係日數, B2 係人數,<br />\n當 A1 係 7 日, B2 一個人頭, 佢就會計 日數*人頭, 係C3 格出答案</blockquote><br />\n=B2*(MIN(MAX(0,A1-0),7)*20+MIN(MAX(0,A1-7),7)*40+MIN(MAX(0,A1-14),7)*60+MAX(0,A1-21)*80)</blockquote><br />\n巴打我用你條式去做, <br />\nA1 日數: 7 日<br />\nB2 人數: 1 人<br />\nC3 收費: 20 &lt;- 呢個係 1 人收費, 如果 B2 係 2 人,<br />\n               呢格就會係 40<br />\n<br />\n但我用你條式, 佢計出黎 C3 一人情況下變左 560 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪有野搞錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果個係<br />\nA1 = 日<br />\nB2 = 人<br />\nC3 = 佢 total 要比幾多錢<br />\n<br />\ne.g.<br />\n7日, 1人, =&gt; 7*20 = 140<br />\n8日, 2人, =&gt; (7*20+1*40)*2 = 360"}]}